A few centuries last week, a man named Adam Threshold was roaming northern iraq when he came across a polo mint, he then went home to dudley due to fear of assassination. He often visits his local mosque to pickett, one sunday he ventured to the mosque, he saw his neighbour trevor fixation. He often spoke with trevor over the inflation of preston north end season tickets. Adam went over to trevor expecting a nice normal conversation, “hello” adam said politely but in a predatory manor, “ i need you to be there for me, i need you to be the person you tucks my bread rolls into bed at night, i want you to be the person to fuck my personal cheese before i eat it”. Adam stool still, in horror, but also feeling quite sexual, he often fucked personal gammon joints for his ex. “ i cant do that, i have 7 kids and 3 wives, i cant leave that all behind, its not what a threshold would do”, trevor swiftly replied, becoming more erect as the seconds went by, “ in return, i will purchase you a scratchcard every 15th tuesday, i will also seductively cook you the vermin i slay throughout the day” adam found himself not only agreeing, but felating trevor at an alarming speed, before long trevor had excreted his sauce all over the window, adams family looking on in disbelief as they all watched spiderman 3 on portable dvd players. Watching through the spunk stained window, the 3 wives swifly fought to the death, the victor, stole several eggcups and countless rice grains.




Adam Threshold wasn’t fully aware of the scope of this scheme though, blissfully unaware, unaware to the point he lost consciousness briefly. Adam was in grave danger, dangerous graves were only some of the grave dangers in store for him, but for an engraver like Adam the danger was only too intriguing.




This ‘scheme’ that the family concoted had 4 stages, stage 1 was induction via a tainted copy of spiderman 3. Stage 3 is using the climate juice and distillating it to get thick climate sauce Stage 4 Requires listening to the heartbeat of a tame badger, giving it a quick stroke and then executing it and hurling its limp body into the chimney of an impoverished family on christmas morning.




“Now, that might sound like a lot of work, but at the end of the day, theres nothing like a tuesday heist, i would often rob recently opened cans of 7up from jews on tuesday, as i was about to leave, i would shit into my hands and smear it onto the walls and my lips, waiting for the family to come home, before removing each persons kneecaps with grenades, and forcing them to watch loose women whilst eating each member behind” trevor grumbled whilst rocking rather disturbingly at the dinner table. “Watch out, youll drop your carrot” adam exclaimed. Trevor sat boss-eyed. This series of events can be described as disturbing, he reached for his phone, opening the spotify application, before long, he had put on beerus by ksi and randolph. Adam was seen running toward the canal, no thoughts in his head but escaping, unfortunately trevor followed him with the song still playing, adam knew he couldnt get away, so he accepted his fate died later that night of severe nosebleeds.
